#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_unveil
msgid "Explore our vast collection and find your next great read."
msgstr "ສຳຫຼວດຄັງສະສົມອັນມະຫາສານຂອງພວກເຮົາ ແລະ ຊອກຫາການອ່ານທີ່ດີຢ້ຽມຄັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_card_offset
msgid ""
"Explore our vast collection of books, magazines, and music. From classic "
"literature to contemporary media, our library offers something for every "
"curious mind."
msgstr ""
"ສຳຫຼວດຄັງສະສົມປຶ້ມ, ວາລະສານ ແລະ ສຽງເພງອັນຫຼາກຫຼາຍຂອງພວກເຮົາ. ຕັ້ງແຕ່ວັນນະຄະດີຄລາສສິກ "
"ຈົນເຖິງສື່ສະໄໝໃໝ່, ຫ້ອງສະໝຸດຂອງພວກເຮົາມີສິ່ງທີ່ໜ້າສົນໃຈສຳລັບທຸກຄົນ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_cards_grid
msgid ""
"Explore the untold stories and hidden truths behind social media profiles. "
"This eye-opening book reveals the realities behind online personas and the "
"contrast with what remains unshared."
msgstr ""
"ສຳຫຼວດເລື່ອງລາວທີ່ບໍ່ເຄີຍຖືກເລົ່າ ແລະ ຄວາມຈິງທີ່ເຊື່ອງໄວ້ເບື້ອງຫຼັງໂປຣຟາຍໂຊຊຽວມີເດຍ. "
"ປຶ້ມຫົວນີ້ຈະເປີດເຜີຍຄວາມຈິງເບື້ອງຫຼັງຕົວຕົນໃນໂລກອອນລາຍ ແລະ ຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງຈາກສິ່ງທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກເຜີຍແຜ່."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_accordion_image
msgid ""
"Find quick answers to common questions about our books, services and "
"policies."
msgstr ""
"ຊອກຫາຄຳຕອບທີ່ວ່ອງໄວສຳລັບຄຳຖາມທີ່ພົບເລື້ອຍກ່ຽວກັບປຶ້ມ, ການບໍລິການ ແລະ ນະໂຍບາຍຂອງພວກເຮົາ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_images_mosaic
msgid "Find your next great read with our newest arrivals and bestsellers."
msgstr "ຊອກຫາປຶ້ມດີໆທີ່ຈະອ່ານເຫຼັ້ມຕໍ່ໄປຈາກປຶ້ມມາໃໝ່ ແລະ ປຶ້ມຂາຍດີຂອງພວກເຮົາ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_key_images
msgid "Finely hand-picked by our most avid readers"
msgstr "ຄັດສັນມາຢ່າງພິຖີພິຖັນໂດຍນັກອ່ານຕົວຢົງຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_accordion_image
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "ຄຳຖາມທີ່ພົບເລື້ອຍ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"George Orwell's dystopian novel depicting a totalitarian society under "
"constant surveillance, and the fight for freedom."
msgstr ""
"ນະວະນິຍາຍແນວ ດິສໂທເປຍ (dystopian) ຂອງ George Orwell "
"ທີ່ພັນລະນາເຖິງສັງຄົມຜະເດັດການທີ່ຖືກຕິດຕາມຢູ່ສະເໝີ ແລະ ການຕໍ່ສູ້ເພື່ອອິດສະລະພາບ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_text_cover
msgid "Get started"
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນເລີຍ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_numbers
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_numbers_showcase
msgid "Happy customers"
msgstr "ລູກຄ້າທີ່ມີຄວາມສຸກ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Harper Lee's Pulitzer Prize-winning novel, a profound story about racial "
"injustice and moral growth in the American South."
msgstr ""
"ນະວະນິຍາຍເຈົ້າຂອງລາງວັນພູລິສເຊີ (Pulitzer Prize) ໂດຍ Harper Lee, "
"ເລື່ອງລາວທີ່ເລິກເຊິ່ງກ່ຽວກັບຄວາມບໍ່ຍຸຕິທຳທາງເຊື້ອຊາດ ແລະ ການເຕີບໂຕທາງສິນລະທຳໃນພາກໃຕ້ຂອງອາເມລິກາ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_showcase
msgid "Hidden Treasures"
msgstr "ຊັບສົມບັດທີ່ເຊື່ອງໄວ້"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid "Horror"
msgstr "ສະຍອງຂວັນ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_bookstore.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ລະຫັດ (ID)"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_cover
msgid "Immerse yourself <br/>in original universes"
msgstr "ດຳດິ່ງ <br/>ສູ່ຈັກກະວານແຫ່ງຕົ້ນສະບັບ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_striped_center_top
msgid ""
"Immerse yourself in a rich collection of books, magazines, and media that "
"inspire learning, imagination, and creativity."
msgstr ""
"ດຳດິ່ງສູ່ຄັງສະສົມປຶ້ມ, ວາລະສານ ແລະ ສື່ຕ່າງໆທີ່ຈະສ້າງແຮງບັນດານໃຈໃນການຮຽນຮູ້, ຈິນຕະນາການ ແລະ "
"ຄວາມຄິດສ້າງສັນ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_carousel_intro
msgid ""
"Immerse yourself in a vast selection of books that spark imagination and "
"offer insight, tailored to every reader's taste."
msgstr ""
"ດຳດິ່ງສູ່ໂລກແຫ່ງປຶ້ມອັນຫຼາກຫຼາຍທີ່ຈະຈຸດປະກາຍຈິນຕະນາການ ແລະ ໃຫ້ແງ່ຄິດ, "
"ຄັດສັນມາໃຫ້ເໝາະກັບລົດນິຍົມຂອງນັກອ່ານທຸກຄົນ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_quadrant
msgid ""
"Immerse yourself in our vast collection of books and music. From timeless "
"classics to contemporary works, we offer a sanctuary for the literary and "
"musical soul.<br/><br/> Find your next inspiration here."
msgstr ""
"ດຳດິ່ງສູ່ຄັງສະສົມປຶ້ມ ແລະ ສຽງເພງອັນມະຫາສານຂອງພວກເຮົາ. ຕັ້ງແຕ່ປຶ້ມຄລາສສິກຕະຫຼອດການ "
"ຈົນເຖິງຜົນງານສະໄໝໃໝ່, ພວກເຮົາເປັນບ່ອນພັກພິງສຳລັບຈິດວິນຍານທີ່ຮັກໃນວັນນະຄະດີ ແລະ ດົນຕີ.<br/><br/> "
"ຄົ້ນຫາແຮງບັນດານໃຈຄັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ທີ່ນີ້."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_cards_grid
msgid ""
"Immerse yourself in the grandeur and intrigue of ancient Rome through richly "
"detailed storytelling. Experience the intricate lives and societal dynamics "
"of one of history's most fascinating civilizations."
msgstr ""
"ດຳດິ່ງສູ່ຄວາມຍິ່ງໃຫຍ່ ແລະ ເລື່ອງລາວທີ່ໜ້າສົນໃຈຂອງໂຣມັນບູຮານ ຜ່ານການເລົ່າເລື່ອງທີ່ມີລາຍລະອຽດຄົບຖ້ວນ. "
"ສຳຜັດກັບຊີວິດທີ່ຊັບຊ້ອນ ແລະ ການປ່ຽນແປງຂອງສັງຄົມໃນໜຶ່ງໃນອາະລິຍະທຳທີ່ໜ້າຕື່ນຕາຕື່ນໃຈທີ່ສຸດໃນປະຫວັດສາດ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_empowerment
msgid "Join our book club"
msgstr "ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມຊົມລົມນັກອ່ານຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_numbers_showcase
msgid "Join our community of thousands of happy and satisfied readers."
msgstr "ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງຊຸມຊົນນັກອ່ານທີ່ພໍໃຈ ແລະ ມີຄວາມສຸກກວ່າພັນຄົນ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_key_benefits
msgid ""
"Join us for author signings, readings, and special events that connect you "
"with the literary community."
msgstr ""
"ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມກິດຈະກຳເຊັນປຶ້ມໂດຍນັກຂຽນ, ການອ່ານປຶ້ມ ແລະ ກິດຈະກຳພິເສດທີ່ຈະເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ທ່ານເຂົ້າກັບຊຸມຊົນນັກອ່ານ "
"ແລະ ນັກຂຽນ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_striped_center_top
msgid "Knowledge curated with care"
msgstr "ຄວາມຮູ້ທີ່ຄັດສັນມາດ້ວຍຄວາມໃສ່ໃຈ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_image_text
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Learn about the difficulties encountered by NASA engineers in sending the "
"first men to Mars."
msgstr ""
"ຮຽນຮູ້ກ່ຽວກັບຄວາມຫຍຸ້ງຍາກທີ່ວິສະວະກອນ NASA ຕ້ອງຜະເຊີນ ໃນການສົ່ງມະນຸດກຸ່ມທຳອິດໄປຍັງດາວອັງຄານ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_features_wall
msgid "Literary Events and Signings"
msgstr "ກິດຈະກຳທາງວັນນະຄະດີ ແລະ ການເຊັນປຶ້ມ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_masonry_block_default_template
msgid "Meet great people"
msgstr "ພົບກັບຜູ້ຄົນທີ່ໜ້າສົນໃຈ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Michelle Obama's inspiring memoir, sharing her personal journey from "
"childhood to her role as First Lady of the United States."
msgstr ""
"ບັນທຶກຄວາມຊົງຈຳທີ່ສ້າງແຮງບັນດານໃຈຂອງ Michelle Obama, "
"ບອກເລົ່າການເດີນທາງຊີວິດສ່ວນຕົວຕັ້ງແຕ່ໄວເດັກ ຈົນເຖິງບົດບາດສຸພາບສະຕີໝາຍເລກໜຶ່ງຂອງສະຫະລັດ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_numbers_showcase
msgid "Numbers speak by themselves"
msgstr "ຕົວເລກບົ່ງບອກເຖິງຄວາມສຳເລັດດ້ວຍຕົວມັນເອງ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_image_text
msgid "Once upon a time..."
msgstr "ຄັ້ງໜຶ່ງດົນນານມາແລ້ວ..."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_key_images
msgid "Our bestsellers of the moment"
msgstr "ປຶ້ມຂາຍດີທີ່ສຸດຂອງພວກເຮົາໃນຕອນນີ້"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_key_benefits
msgid ""
"Our knowledgeable staff provides tailored book suggestions, helping you "
"discover new favorites that match your taste."
msgstr ""
"ພະນັກງານທີ່ມີຄວາມຮູ້ຂອງພວກເຮົາ ພ້ອມໃຫ້ຄຳແນະນຳປຶ້ມທີ່ເໝາະສົມກັບທ່ານ, "
"ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານຄົ້ນພົບປຶ້ມເຫຼັ້ມໃໝ່ທີ່ກົງກັບລົດນິຍົມຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_features_wall
msgid "Our other services"
msgstr "ບໍລິການອື່ນໆຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_showcase
msgid ""
"Own literary masterpieces without breaking the bank. Your favorite classic "
"books at budget-friendly prices."
msgstr ""
"ເປັນເຈົ້າຂອງຜົນງານວັນນະຄະດີຊິ້ນເອກໄດ້ໃນລາຄາທີ່ປະຢັດ. ປຶ້ມຄລາສສິກທີ່ທ່ານມັກ ໃນລາຄາທີ່ເປັນກັນເອງ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_key_benefits
msgid "Personalized Recommendations"
msgstr "ຄຳແນະນຳສະເພາະບຸກຄົນ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_showcase
msgid ""
"Prime quality second-hand books, carefully selected for value and charm. "
"Timeless stories at great prices."
msgstr ""
"ປຶ້ມມືສອງຄຸນນະພາບດີ, ຄັດສັນມາຢ່າງພິຖີພິຖັນເພື່ອໃຫ້ໄດ້ທັງຄຸນຄ່າ ແລະ ສະເໜ່. "
"ເລື່ອງລາວຕະຫຼອດການໃນລາຄາທີ່ຄຸ້ມຄ່າ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_text_image
msgid "Probably your next <br/>favorite book"
msgstr "ອາດຈະເປັນປຶ້ມ <br/>ເຫຼັ້ມຕໍ່ໄປທີ່ທ່ານມັກ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_wavy_grid
msgid "Quality and Selection"
msgstr "ຄຸນນະພາບ ແລະ ການຄັດສັນ"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_three_columns
msgid "Re-edition"
msgstr "ພິມຄືນໃໝ່"

#. module: theme_bookstore
