msgstr "The Great Gatsby"

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"The first re-edition of this Latin dictionary, from 1460. Printed originally "
"on the Gutenberg press."
msgstr ""
"ການພິມຄືນໃໝ່ຄັ້ງທຳອິດຂອງວັດຈະນານຸກົມພາສາລາຕິນນີ້ ຈາກປີ 1460. ພິມຄັ້ງທຳອິດດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງພິມ Gutenberg."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bookstore.s_title
msgid ""
"The most beautiful things in the world cannot be seen or touched, they are "
"felt with the heart."
msgstr "ສິ່ງທີ່ສວຍງາມທີ່ສຸດໃນໂລກບໍ່ອາດເຫັນໄດ້ດ້ວຍຕາ ຫຼື ສຳຜັດໄດ້ດ້ວຍມື, ແຕ່ຕ້ອງຮັບຮູ້ດ້ວຍຫົວໃຈ."

#. module: theme_bookstore
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_bookstore.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືຮູບແບບ (Theme Utils)"

#. module: theme_bookstore
